41
00:04:33,663 --> 00:04:34,863
Huh?

42
00:04:34,963 --> 00:04:37,696
Ayolah, Robert.

43
00:04:37,795 --> 00:04:40,529
Jangan berlagak suci, jangan.

44
00:04:44,327 --> 00:04:46,895
Kau memasang perangkap pada
Edward, dan dia lolos.

45
00:04:46,995 --> 00:04:48,561
Aku pasang perangkap padamu,
dan kau lolos.

46
00:04:48,661 --> 00:04:51,860
Besok kau pasang perangkap padaku,
dan aku lolos.

47
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:55,593
Dan begitu seterusnya
sampai kita berdua menua,

48
00:04:55,693 --> 00:04:57,325
