87
00:07:27,467 --> 00:07:31,100
<i>Pertempuran hebat terjadi,
keduanya mahir,</i>

88
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,600
<i>kedua melawan sengit.</i>

89
00:07:36,233 --> 00:07:41,799
Mereka bertarung demi mahkota,
demi keunggulan klan mereka,

90
00:07:41,899 --> 00:07:46,431
dan demi masa depan Skotlandia.

91
00:07:46,531 --> 00:07:49,231
