163
00:14:39,595 --> 00:14:41,095
Kita selesai disini.

164
00:15:07,690 --> 00:15:09,557
Kalian jalanlah sendiri, anak-anak.

165
00:15:21,688 --> 00:15:23,021
Tapi selesaikan pekerjaan dulu, Hamish.

166
00:15:23,121 --> 00:15:25,587
Coba siapkan umpan di kailnya dulu,
dia memakannya.

167
00:15:25,687 --> 00:15:29,721
